{"synckey":1695622419,"updated":[{"bookId":"23691364","bookmarkId":"23691364_32_920-969","createTime":1689609095,"chapterUid":109,"colorStyle":2,"type":1,"markText":"以不同的速度训练，可以锻炼你身体的所有主要能量供应系统。因此，你的训练应该在各种不同的速度下进行。","range":"871-920"},{"bookId":"23691364","bookmarkId":"23691364_15_1587-1639","chapterUid":92,"markText":"从生物力学方面讲，当你以脚跟着地时，实际上是给自己踩了一脚刹车，优秀的运动员是不会跑一步踩一下刹车的。”","range":"1458-1510","createTime":1589705649,"type":1},{"bookId":"23691364","bookmarkId":"23691364_13_822-953","chapterUid":90,"markText":"在慢跑时，这个负荷可以增加到体重的1.5倍，全速跑时可以增加到3倍。如果你体重是90公斤，你必须要使你的身体，包括你的肌肉、肌腱、韧带和骨骼能够承受从慢跑时135公斤至全速跑时270公斤的负荷。一个运动员如果没有足够的身体力量作为基础，不可能完成正确的技术动作。","range":"774-905","createTime":1589705547,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"26 全能训练计划 5公里，10公里，半马，全马","chapterUid":109,"chapterIdx":32},{"title":"09 第一课 脚","chapterUid":92,"chapterIdx":15},{"title":"07 力量训练 4种常规的力量练习","chapterUid":90,"chapterIdx":13}],"book":{"bookId":"23691364","version":714773213,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/12/yuewen_23691364/s_yuewen_236913641695278016.jpg","title":"姿势跑法：跑得更快，更有效率，不受伤的跑步方法","author":"尼可拉斯·罗曼诺夫 寇特·布伦加","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KcL.oLaKD%UEjEIU|Zr?aJ","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#370e18"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#3f0217"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#480017"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#4d2528"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#571d24"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#620f20"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#693b38"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#743331"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#80292a"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#95001d"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#8f4d48"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#a63c38"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#825450"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#c4584f"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#9b6e69"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#b76058"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#b58983"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#c4827a"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#d27c71"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#ec6b5e"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#ef9689"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#fd8e80"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#ff8576"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#ebbdb6"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#fdb7ac"},{"key":"8/12","hex